			<p>Posted in <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/category/autobiographical/" rel="category tag">Autobiographical</a>, <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/category/soul-assassins/" rel="category tag">Soul Assassins</a></p>
			<p>Tagged with <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/tag/afrika-bambaataa/" rel="tag">Afrika Bambaataa</a>, <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/tag/al-gore/" rel="tag">Al Gore</a>, <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/tag/bob-brandel/" rel="tag">Bob Brandel</a>, <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/tag/brian-moores/" rel="tag">Brian Moores</a>, <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/tag/brian-spaeth/" rel="tag">Brian Spaeth</a>, <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/tag/david-bither/" rel="tag">David Bither</a>, <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/tag/fleshtones/" rel="tag">Fleshtones</a>, <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/tag/flick-ford/" rel="tag">Flick Ford</a>, <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/tag/horizon-magazine/" rel="tag">Horizon magazine</a>, <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/tag/inconvenient-truth/" rel="tag">Inconvenient Truth</a>, <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/tag/jeff-peisch/" rel="tag">Jeff Peisch</a>, <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/tag/laurie-david/" rel="tag">Laurie David</a>, <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/tag/lyres/" rel="tag">Lyres</a>, <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/tag/rick-dehaan/" rel="tag">Rick Dehaan</a>, <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/tag/soul-assassins/" rel="tag">Soul Assassins</a>, <a href="http://stevenhager420.wordpress.com/tag/steven-hager/" rel="tag">Steven Hager</a></p>		</div>
